# Environment Variables Configuration for Azure App Service
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual API keys

# OpenAI API Key (Required for OpenAI models)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# OpenRouter API Key (Required for Gemini models)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# YouTube Data API Key (Required for data fetching feature)
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=your_youtube_api_key_here

# For Azure App Service deployment, set these as Application Settings instead of .env file:
# 1. Go to Azure Portal > App Service > Configuration > Application settings
# 2. Add new application setting for each environment variable above
# 3. Restart the App Service after adding all settings